2   Ore pee eishunye nkolong'i ile nerik Yesu Petero o Yakobo o Yohana, neilepie enchumata o ldoinyo oado aa ninche ake; newala emua enye edolita ninche. 
3  Neitintilu lkilani lenyena, aaiborru oleng, enaa meetae olaisujani te nkop oidim aiborrie metotiwuo neijia. 
4  Neliooyu Eliya o Musa te dukuya ninche; eirorie Yesu. 
5  Newalu Petero nejoki Yesu, “Olaiteng'enani, aisidai kitii ene; nchoo iyiook kishetu ilng'oborri okuni, olino obo o le Musa obo o le Eliya obo.” 
6  Naa aimeyiolo enajoito, amu eiputukunyo oleng.


7   Neitemoo enkatampoi nejo, “Nele Oinoti lai lanyor, ninye entoning.” 
8  Ore nabo kata ake, ejo maing'orisho neitu eitoki aadol likae otii te nebo ninche. Yesu ake openy. 
9  Ore edou to ldoinyo, neitanap amitiki einosaki likae tung'ani nena naatoduaa ninche, o metaba naa nepiu Enkerai e Tung'ani aing'uaa ilootuata.


10  Neibung ninche ilo rorei, neikilikuana maate aajo. “Ainyoo doi ena najo ake, kepiu aing'uaa ilootuata?” 
11   Neikilikuan ninche Yesu aajoki, “Ainyoo pee ejo ilaiteng'enak loo nkitanapat eji meeta nchere meng'as Eliya alotu?” 
12  Newaliki Yesu ajoki ninche, “Esipa eng'as Eliya alotu neitang'ejuk imbaa pooki. Paa amaa, ainyoo pee ejo lkigerot ti alo Enkerai e Tung'ani, eji keitamei too mbaa kumok nemenuni? 
13  Kake ajoki nanu intae, eewuo Eliya, neitaas ninche ninye enapa ake nayieu neitaas, anaa enatisirakaki ninye.”

