33  Nepuonu Kapernaum; ore etii Yesu aji neikilikuan ninche ajoki, “Ainyoo naaji enchankar niaatata te nkoitoi?” 
34   Negira ninche; amu keishankarrate aajo kalo olkitok te pooki. 
35   Neton neipot lelo tomon o aare; nejoki ninche, “Ore oloyieu neaku ole dukuya, nchoo metaa ninye obayie te pooki neaku osinka le pooki.” 
36  Nedumu enkerai, neitasheyie te mpolos enye; nedumu aibung too nkaik enyena nejoki ninche, 
37   “Ore pooki ong'amu enkerai anaa ena te nkarna ai, nanu eng'amu; ore olaang'amu, neme nanu ake eng'amu kake ilo laairriwua.”

